(2, 1, '2016-11-30 04:15:32', '2016-11-30 04:15:32', '<div class="entry-header">\r\n\r\nWant to get involved? Want to make a difference in people’s lives? Want to network with business professionals? Then consider joining Literacy Chicago’s Associate Board. Come to our open house on Wednesday December 7th to learn more and meet our current members.\r\n\r\nDate: Wednesday December 7th\r\nTime” 6pm – 7:30pm\r\nLocation: 641 W. Lake Street, Suite 200 , Chicago, IL 60661\r\n\r\nRegister Today!: <a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/literacy-chicago-open-house-tickets-29266483841">https://www.eventbrite.com/e/literacy-chicago-open-house-tickets-29266483841</a>\r\n\r\nLiteracy Chicago is currently seeking energetic volunteer junior board members to join their active junior board. Literacy Chicago is a nonprofit that empowers individuals to achieve greater self-sufficiency through language and literacy instruction. Applicants should have some experience in nonprofits, marketing, fundraising, and be able to make a commitment of at least a year. Junior board members will coordinate and execute small fundraisers, assist in volunteer opportunities within the agency, and perform other tasks as needed. Meetings are held twice a month on Wednesday evenings.\r\n\r\nTo apply, send your resume and a letter of interest to <a href="mailto:rdominguez@literacychicago.org">rdominguez@literacychicago.org</a>.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Get Involved', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'get-involved', '', '', '2017-02-01 20:05:02', '2017-02-01 20:05:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
